        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The NIRMAN SHRAMIK AUZAAR TOOLKIT SAHAYATA YOJANA is a social welfare scheme launched by the Government of Jharkhand to provide financial assistance to registered construction workers in the state for the purchase of essential tools and equipment required for their work.\n<br>\n\n> **Objectives**\n\n\n1. To improve the working conditions and productivity of construction workers in Jharkhand.\n1. To reduce the financial burden on construction workers for purchasing essential tools and equipment.\n1. To promote the overall socio-economic development of construction workers in the state.\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "> Actual cost of purchasing tools/toolkit or ₹ 2,000/-, whichever is less\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "",
