      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a native of the Rajasthan state.\n1. The applicant must be a registered construction worker for 3 years.\n1. Amount payable only on purchasing tools/toolkits related to one&#39;s work or business.\n1. The purchase of tools/toolkits will be done by the construction worker himself and the bill is required to be attached to the application.\n\n",
